{"tid":519583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有得俾你揀，你會唔會選擇出世？","createTime":"2018-01-04T13:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T10:28:03.000Z","uid":150216,"like":118,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"559ed85848ef6de7d18baa51150043302fd925df","tid":519583,"uid":150216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"俾我就一定唔會<br />\n無論喺香港定係外國<br />\n有錢定係冇錢我都唔會<br />\n生命嘅本質就係受苦<br />\n人類本性就係無止境追求<br />\n不停耗用地球資源<br />\n(生而為人，我很抱歉)<br />\n名、利、金錢<br />\n就算坐擁好多錢都不斷貪<br />\n又要同其他人social帶假面具<br />\n好啦俾你成功左<br />\n最後幾年俾病魔折磨都係要死<br />\n你可能會話世界咁靚、好多嘢都好美好<br />\n但其實空虛同死亡先係永遠<br />\n人一生用盡一切辦法求生<br />\n泯滅一切真善美搬來短暫嘅生存<br />\n但死亡先至係永遠<br />\n咁不如一開始咩都唔好擁有<br />\n咁咪達至何處惹塵埃嘅無爭境界<br />\n有冇人同我一樣咁諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想出世<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想出世去體驗世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(純粹想知大家點諗，講定先:投我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"567045be7a154845e6a9f19274c06fb2d005f02e","tid":519583,"uid":150216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d6f684f6d02b7ff85318f27befc770d697baf03","tid":519583,"uid":69140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:38:29.000Z","msg":"人生好苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dfe39bdf34ea73b78e6f547173afa785a951612","tid":519583,"uid":150216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"42f9003024b1ccabc8bee1462125c2f0abeca9dc","tid":519583,"uid":1255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:40:14.000Z","msg":"窮就緊係唔出啦"},{"pid":"001c552a4893acdd00f7ebbb0998eb3c111fb830","tid":519583,"uid":150216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42f9003024b1ccabc8bee1462125c2f0abeca9dc","tid":519583,"uid":1255,"like"